---
import { Anchor } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="about-section" class="py-24 bg-vintage-50 relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-center">
  <!-- Background Decor -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-30">
     <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-secondary/5 rounded-full blur-[128px]"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cream-paper.png')] opacity-40 mix-blend-multiply"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
         <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-vintage-200 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-secondary rotate-45 shadow-md">
            <Anchor className="w-8 h-8 text-secondary -rotate-45" />
         </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-primary mb-8 leading-tight">Biz Kimiz?</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed font-serif font-light mb-12 italic relative">
        <span class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 text-6xl text-secondary/20 font-serif">"</span>
        Düşünce ve Kitap Topluluğu, entelektüel üretimin tüketimden daha değerli olduğuna inananların limanıdır. 
        Amacımız, fikirlerin çarpıştığı ama asla incitmediği, derinliğin sığlığa galip geldiği bir alan yaratmaktır.
        <span class="absolute -bottom-12 -right-4 text-6xl text-secondary/20 font-serif">"</span>
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 border-t-2 border-secondary/10 pt-12">
          <div>
             <span class="block text-3xl font-bold font-serif text-primary mb-2">5K+</span>
             <span class="text-sm font-mono text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest">Aktif Üye</span>
          </div>
          <div>
             <span class="block text-3xl font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-2">120+</span>
             <span class="text-sm font-mono text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest">Atölye</span>
          </div>
           <div>
             <span class="block text-3xl font-bold font-serif text-primary mb-2">850+</span>
             <span class="text-sm font-mono text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest">Analiz</span>
          </div>
           <div>
             <span class="block text-3xl font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-2">∞</span>
             <span class="text-sm font-mono text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest">Fikir</span>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</section>
